                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>üîç Smart Detection Engine</h3>
              <p>
                Our intelligent scanning engine automatically detects development tools 
                and their cache locations across your system. No manual configuration needed.
              </p>
              <ul class="feature-benefits">
                <li>Automatic tool discovery</li>
                <li>Multi-threaded scanning for speed</li>
                <li>Deep directory analysis</li>
                <li>Safe file identification</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-highlight reverse">
